      "span_text": "The initiation codon AUG of atpB mRNA was then altered to GUG and, as a control, the AUG initiation codon of atpE mRNA which possesses a functional SD sequence [GGAG;  ] was replaced by GUG. As shown in Figure 4B , the mutant atpE mRNA was translated at 10% of the control efficiency, whereas no translation was observed from the mutant atpB mRNA. This indicates that the AUG codon itself is one of the essential determinants for translation of atpB mRNAs.",
